#### In this lesson, students learn the importance of data cleaning and the key functions used to identify and handle data quality issues, including isnull(), isnull().sum(), dropna(), fillna(), and value_counts(). 
#### Through a series of investigate and modify levels, they explore how to evaluate datasets, identify missing, invalid, and inconsistent data, and apply techniques to clean the data. 

